---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import InstallBox from "../components/InstallBox.astro";
import { product } from "../data/product";
---
<BaseLayout title="文档 — Pipee" description="安装并使用 Pipee，开发 Pi Extension。"><div class="page"><section class="content-hero pad"><span class="eyebrow">Documentation</span><div><h1>安装、启动，然后继续使用 Pi。</h1><p>Pipee 是本地 Web UI。这里先完成产品安装，再分别说明 Pi Extension 与可选 Web Surface。</p></div></section><div class="docs-layout pad"><aside><div><span>开始</span><a href="#install">安装 Pipee</a><a href="#run">启动与连接</a></div><div><span>开发</span><a href="#model">概念边界</a><a href="#first">第一个 Extension</a><a href="#surface">Web Surface</a></div><div><span>更多</span><a href="/trust">信任边界</a><a href="/developers">开发者入口</a></div></aside><article>
  <section id="install"><span class="chapter">01 / INSTALL</span><h2>全局安装 Pipee</h2><p>推荐使用 pnpm 全局安装。安装一次后，可以在任意项目目录启动。</p><InstallBox/><div class="note"><strong>安装边界</strong><p><code>{product.packageName}</code> 只安装 Web UI，不会迁移或复制你的 Pi Session。</p></div></section>
  <section id="run"><span class="chapter">02 / RUN</span><h2>启动本地 Web UI</h2><p>进入希望工作的项目目录，运行：</p><div class="code-block"><header><span>Terminal</span><button type="button" data-copy={product.cli}>复制</button></header><pre>{product.cli}</pre></div><p>Pipee 启动本地服务，并连接当前机器上的 Pi 工作环境。</p></section>
  <section id="model"><span class="chapter">03 / MODEL</span><h2>三个概念，不混用</h2><div class="concepts"><div><strong>Pi</strong><span>Agent runtime</span><p>拥有 Session、模型、上下文和 Extension API。</p></div><div><strong>Pi Extension</strong><span>Runtime capability</span><p>拥有工具、事件、状态、服务和生命周期。</p></div><div><strong>Pipee</strong><span>Web UI</span><p>呈现 Pi，并承载 Extension 声明的可选界面。</p></div></div></section>
  <section id="first"><span class="chapter">04 / FIRST EXTENSION</span><h2>创建 Pi Extension</h2><p>Extension 首先必须作为 Pi 运行时能力独立成立。</p><div class="code-block"><header><span>src/extension.ts</span><span>Pi Extension</span></header><pre><span class="syntax">export default function</span> (pi: ExtensionAPI) &#123;
  pi.registerTool(&#123;
    name: <span class="string">"hello_pipee"</span>,
    description: <span class="string">"返回一个问候"</span>,
    parameters: Type.Object(&#123;&#125;),
    async execute() &#123; /* ... */ &#125;
  &#125;)
&#125;</pre></div></section>
  <section id="surface"><span class="chapter">05 / OPTIONAL WEB SURFACE</span><h2>需要页面时，再接入 Pipee</h2><p>Web Surface 是同一 Extension package 的可选资源。核心行为不能依赖 Pipee 才成立。</p><div class="code-block"><header><span>package.json</span><span>Optional</span></header><pre><span class="string">"piSuite"</span>: &#123;
  <span class="string">"web"</span>: &#123;
    <span class="string">"contract"</span>: <span class="string">"pi-suite/web-surface@1"</span>,
    <span class="string">"document"</span>: <span class="string">"./dist/web/index.html"</span>
  &#125;
&#125;</pre></div><a class="button dark end-link" href="/developers">继续阅读开发指南 <span>→</span></a></section>
</article></div></div></BaseLayout>
<script>document.querySelectorAll<HTMLButtonElement>("[data-copy]").forEach((button)=>button.addEventListener("click",async()=>{await navigator.clipboard.writeText(button.dataset.copy??"");button.textContent="已复制 ✓";window.setTimeout(()=>button.textContent="复制",1400)}));</script>
<style>.docs-layout{display:grid;gap:70px;grid-template-columns:190px minmax(0,760px);justify-content:space-between;padding-bottom:120px;padding-top:70px}.docs-layout>aside{align-self:start;position:sticky;top:100px}.docs-layout aside div{display:flex;flex-direction:column;margin-bottom:27px}.docs-layout aside span{color:var(--dim);font:700 8px var(--mono);letter-spacing:.09em;margin-bottom:8px;text-transform:uppercase}.docs-layout aside a{border-left:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);font-size:11px;padding:7px 11px}.docs-layout aside a:hover{border-color:var(--blue);color:var(--ink)}.docs-layout article{min-width:0}.docs-layout article>section{border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);margin-bottom:78px;padding-bottom:78px;scroll-margin-top:95px}.chapter{color:var(--blue);font:700 8px var(--mono);letter-spacing:.1em}.docs-layout h2{font-size:clamp(36px,4.3vw,50px);letter-spacing:-.06em;line-height:1.05;margin:20px 0}.docs-layout article>section>p{color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;line-height:1.85}.docs-layout :global(.install-box){margin-top:25px;max-width:none}.note{background:#eeeeeb;border-radius:8px;margin-top:18px;padding:19px}.note strong{font-size:11px}.note p{color:var(--muted);font-size:11px;line-height:1.7;margin:7px 0 0}.code-block{margin-top:25px}.code-block header button{background:transparent;border:0;color:#8da7ff;cursor:pointer;font:700 8px var(--mono)}.concepts{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);margin-top:30px}.concepts>div{border:1px solid var(--line);margin-left:-1px;padding:20px}.concepts strong,.concepts span{display:block}.concepts strong{font-size:18px}.concepts span{color:var(--blue);font:700 7px var(--mono);margin-top:7px;text-transform:uppercase}.concepts p{color:var(--muted);font-size:10px;line-height:1.7;margin:30px 0 0}.end-link{margin-top:30px}@media(max-width:760px){.docs-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding-top:55px}.docs-layout>aside{display:none}.concepts{grid-template-columns:1fr}.concepts>div{margin:-1px 0 0}}</style>
